def min_moves_to_equal_strings(s: str, t: str) -> int:
    len_s = len(s)
    len_t = len(t)
    min_len = min(len_s, len_t)
    i = 1
    while i < min_len:
        if s[-1 - i] != t[-1 - i]:
            break
        i += 1
    moves = 2 * (min_len - i) + abs(len_s - len_t)
    return moves
